title: Incarnate
description: Welcome to Season Two of the Marked Saga  Preorder Incarnate, the fifth book in the Marked Saga, and join Jemma as she returns to Hollow Hills for her senior year only to be hit with the biggest shock of her life. Unfortunately, her unexpected welcome wagon is the least of her worries when she discovers there's a new evil in town and it's bigger than anything she's ever gone up against before.  Full description coming soon! SCROLL UP TO PREORDER NOW   A Dark Paranormal Romance.
author: Bianca Scardoni
